description: Générer automatiquement des tests unitaires pour extractors
globs:
  - "**/extractors/*.py"
filters:
  - type: event
    pattern: "file_create|file_modify"
actions:
  - type: suggest
    message: |
      1. Utilisez pytest et fixtures pour chaque extractor.
      2. Exemples de tests :
         ```python
         def test_extract_title():
             html = '<h1>Test</h1>'
             assert extract_title(html) == 'Test'
         ```
  - type: execute
    command: |
      pytest --maxfail=1 --disable-warnings -q